text:
Bhai kahan se start karun...pehli baar tujhse mila tha tab sabse pehle hansi aayi thi magar tera confidence dekh ke alag hi hil gaya tha...bhai dussa to aa hi jayegaâ€¦pure first year tere gadde pe soya hun magar tune kabhi mana nhi kiya....teri vajah kitne mast logon se mulakat hui haiâ€¦.esc 101 ki friday class se lekar techkriti ke gin bhi nhi sakta maiâ€¦ kitni baar tu bolta  tha contest dene ke liye...tu akela tha jo hamesha mujhe call karta tha 2nd year intern par...tere london visa ka kitna rr karta thaâ€¦.magar tune trip miss karke achha nhi kiya yaar...is baat ka dukh rhega...second third year mein apane room ke saath apan bhi door ho gye yaar magar help maangne ke liye hamesha ek bande ke paas mai jaa sakta tha vo tu tha...intern ke interviews ke samay bhi tune hi himmat di thi..pure college mein koi bhi tera mazak uda deta tha magar tu bura nhi maanta thaâ€¦.placement aur intern mein to pata nhi kitne anginat logon ki madad ki hai tune yaar...itna helpful aadmi aur koi nhi hai campus mein...sabka entertainment kar sakta hai tu bhai vo bhi just by being yourself....akhiri ke 1.5 mhina tere bina acche nhi hote yaar...aur shuru ke hafte mein kya maze maare the quarantine mein...vahan first year ke baad pehli baar apna agal bagal room rhaâ€¦Jo uss din jo harkat ki maine vo hosh mein nhi karta mai...tujhe pata hai kitni madad ki hai tune and for that Iâ€™ll be forever grateful...uss din sone ke liye bhej dena tha tum logon ko yaar...jo bhi maine bola usmein teri galti nhi thi yaar...
Jab bhi order karne ka mann karta hai sabse pehle teri hi yaad aati hai yaar...College se akhiri baar jaane se pehle tujhse gale mila tab saari college life ka recap mil gaya thaâ€¦.anginat kisse hai kitne hi likhun...Finally tu nhi hota to meri life aaj jo hai vo nhi hoti. 
I hope ki touch mein rhe apan...btw birthday pe tera dance dekhke maza hi aa gya

Bas ab yhi saath yaad ayega bhai! Jaldi milte hai yaar, tu to jaipur aa hi sakta hai flights ke liye...

text: Tere baare mein kya hi kahunâ€¦.kaafi helping banda hai tu...abhi bhi yaad hai mera second sem tere vajah se hi bacha hai varna kon hi apna laptop deta hai bhai...Branch change ke baad mujhe laga hi tha ki tu hi sabse shi banda hai jiske saath mai MTH kaat sakta hun and I wasnâ€™t wrong until the third year lol...Apna ICPC mein nhi hua magar kaafi kuch seekhne ko mila tujhse....jo mai life mein bilkul use karunga....End waale saal mein to agar tu aur vijit nhi hote to shayad hi kaam nikalta...to uske liye thanks...Bas aise hi chapte reh magar apni long distance â€œgirlfriendsâ€ ko phone pe â€œfrench kissesâ€ dena band karde...aur bhai ye sab private mein kiya kar do sone ki acting karne waale harami roomates ke saamne nhi...baaki to mujhe pata hai tu chapega hi magar matlab ke bina bhi call kar liya kar....
author: Aakash  Khandelwal

text:
â€œHey, Hiâ€ , â€œAle liteshâ€
Tera influence meri life pe itna zyada hai ki unhe summarize karne hi kaafi mushkil hai especially emotionally......in 4 saal tujhse jitna seekha hai shayad hi kisi se seekha hogaâ€¦
first year se mera RR khaali tune suna hai...CC/NCL ko merse associate kara magar dikhta to tu bhi tha mujhe...pehle kuch dino se hi pata lag gya tha kitna talented aadmi hai tu...tabhi too itni aasani aur masti mein double dassa maar diya...tera sochne ka tareeka aur priorities sort karna seekha hai maineâ€¦First year ke samay pe mujhe aapka room mate banne ka saubhagya prapt hua aur pata chala ki cooler khareedna kitna difficult haiâ€¦
Mai apne aap ko unlucky samjhta tha yahan aane se pehle magar mere se zyada lucky shayad koi nhi especially because tere jaise dost hai mere paas. Itni positive aur helping banda shayad hi koi hai pure campus meinâ€¦
Kaafi kuch seekha hai magar bed se uthte hi ready kaise hote hai ye ninja technique nhi aayi(mussorie trip). Ek aur trip karni hai yaar tere saath, pata nhi time kaise niklega...vaise agli trip ke liye tip: agar skin cut lag jaye to thoda sehen kar lena lol.  Likhne ko itne kisse aur kahani hai ki novel likhlein magar end mein ek copied shayari se khatam karna chahunga, 

â€œDosti mein dost, dost ka khuda hota hai, mehsoos tab hota hai jab vo juda hota haiâ€
author: Aakash  Khandelwal

text: First 2 saal mein to zyada baat hui nhi apni magar tu hi bhai jiske notes padh kar mai paas hua hoon. Thank you for being so organized and a legible writer. Baaki to saath mein prepare karna aur rote rehna to sab MTH walon mein common hai. Goodluck bhai for your life ahead!!
author: Aakash  Khandelwal

text:
Shayad tujhe utna yaad nhi magar fest ka kaafi time aur baaki bacha puratime maine bas DRS ke saath hi bitaya haiâ€¦.Haan shayad utni dil se dil ka connect first year summer mein akhiri day of the campus hua...presentation se pehle apni puri life suna di maine tujhe...aisa laga ki maano dusra bhai mil gaya hoâ€¦apna to family structure bhi same hi hai...to ig that makes senseâ€¦.Magar uss din ke baad se abhi tak vo connect nhi chuta hai vo kuch kaale 10 din chor ke...Apne dil ki har baat sabse pehle tere se share ki hai yaar aur aj bhi karta hunâ€¦Terse achha poet nhi dekha maine campus mein...mujhe bohot khushi hoti hai jab koi bas apne dimag se koi cheez  hakeekat mein la deta hai...Aur teri poems sun ke vhi khushi ka ehsas hota hai...ye kabhi mat chodnaâ€¦
Asli maza to trip pe aaya tha yaarâ€¦.tere weight ke karan mujhe bhi beech beech mein rukne ka karan mil jaata tha...so thanks for that...
Tune jo 30Kg loose karke mujhe 10k ka chuna lagaya hai uska zyadda dukh nhi hai mujhe magar seekhne ko mila hai ki agar insaan chahe to kuch bhi kar sakta hai..Poster aur ads aur bhi niklenge laga reh aise hiâ€¦
Baaki bhai chinta mat kar nyc chala jayega tu wahan linkedin ka naya office khul rha hai...
author: Aakash  Khandelwal

text: Pehli baar baat apni SG banane ke baad hui thi tabhi pata lag gaya tha kitna mast aadmi haiâ€¦4 saal ka gam nhi bhai, kyonki jab bhi baat hui maza aa gaya ...tumare onspot kahani banane ka to level ekdum pro hai...Shi mein yaar akhiri kuch din especially last din to alag hi maza aa gaya tha yaar...apni baat bolne ka confidence dene ke liye shukriya...Jaldi milenge bhaiâ€¦
author: Aakash  Khandelwal

text: Mere paas tumse pehli baar baat karne se pehle do reference the...ek to shashank ke kisso se aur dusra CC mein Phy103 ki kitab ke saath lad rha ek masoom laundaâ€¦.magar dono references saath mein baithe hi nhi...Jab baat hui tab pata laga kya mast aadmi ho tum...Bhai Hall ki halat kabhi nhi sudharti agar tum na hote toâ€¦.Magar tumhe college aana tha akhiri 1.5 mhine mein yaar saath mein maze karne ka mauka milta. Khair koi nhi agli baar milenge to tumhare thesis topic â€œManaging and directing the gurgling â€˜Rhodesâ€™ â€, pe vistarse charcha karenge...
author: Aakash  Khandelwal

text:
Meri koi ho na ho tu hai meri girlfriend. FIrst year mein to terse baat bhi nhi hui magar jab 2nd year se tujhe jaan ne ka mauka mila aisa laga ki ye connection to kaafi time tak rahega...Bhale hi ICPC mein nhi hua ho magar lifetime guru mil gaya hai mujheâ€¦
Padhai mein hi nhi har jagah jeene ka tareeka sikhaya hai tune...Shayad teri fighting spirit gaming se aati hai magar tu banda bohot hi jabaz hai...apna alag hi path define kiya hia tune...Koi apni life itni jaldi turnaround nhi kar sakta jo tune ki hai aur mujhe pata hai you will be one of the most successful alumni of this college...Not necessarily in terms of money but the life you are going to lead...bas mujhe apni chaya mein rakhnaâ€¦
Tune mujhe tab sambhala jab mujhe laga ki sab khatam ho gaya...Jab bhi tujhe kisi cheez ki zarurat ho, kisi ke saath ki zarurat ho to bas bula lena...Kuch achhe dost hote hai magar you are my family.
author: Aakash  Khandelwal
